'''Krevi''' was a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] concept of loyalty. [[Nek Bwua'tu]] swore an oath of krevi to the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] after becoming a [[Fleet Admiral/Legends|Fleet Admiral]]. This made his loyalty to the Alliance even stronger than his loyalty to [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]] or his people. Even when the Alliance began to fall apart under the leadership of [[Darth Caedus]], Bwua'tu stayed true to his krevi.

